# Bundled embedder weights (~185 MB total: nomic ~150 MB + snowflake ~33 MB).
# Populated by `pnpm --filter @lodestone/ingest bundle-models` (maintainer-only,
# pre-publish). Friends never run that script — they receive the weights via
# the published npm tarball, where `dist/models/` contains the bundled files
# (copied from `models/` by the `build` script).
models/
